{"tid":1056680,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(邊位巴打) 29歲男精神病人擅離青山醫院　警方正接手尋人","createTime":"2019-03-11T11:10:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-11T18:51:10.000Z","uid":45120,"like":81,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":68,"replies":[{"pid":"8cab1b3bacfc91b619b8af48fc221fb153dd9518","tid":1056680,"uid":45120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T11:10:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2290000/2290443/zzzz20040115040_1024_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2290000%2F2290443%2Fzzzz20040115040_1024_1024.jpg&h=baae88f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n醫院管理局稱，青山醫院成人精神科一名29歲住院男病人，今早8時許擅自離開病房，病房職員隨即通知保安員在醫院範圍搜索。該院翻查閉路電視紀錄後，相信該名病人已擅自離開醫院。青山醫院該院非常重視事件，已即時報警，該院會全力配合警方的搜索行動。<br />\n<br />\n該名病人早前入住該院精神科病房，經治療後病情已有改善，正於該院接受精神科康復治療。該名病人身高約1.74米、中等身材、黑色頭髮及配戴眼鏡，當時身穿灰色上衣及黑色長褲。<br />\n<br />\n公眾人士若發現有關病人，請馬上致電62735787通知警方新界北總區失蹤人口調查組或致電青山醫院電話2456 7111。醫院已透過早期事故通報系統向醫院管理局總辦事處呈報事件。該院會繼續與病人家屬聯絡，提供所需協助。"},{"pid":"6ee4b9838c10203f87f44a43f3db5ea4c9c2012e","tid":1056680,"uid":45120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T11:11:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190311/bkn-20190311183821442-0311_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190311%2Fbkn-20190311183821442-0311_00822_001.html&d=JC%2BoF4fRaZyKvWcl7nla%2FAy7VxIBYRqzliHj24KwcnI%3D&h=6d64cbc6\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190311/bkn-20190311183821442-0311_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"0f613e0d3aaa101f6ccb8740ef0e884afa3425a3","tid":1056680,"uid":30081,"like":223,"dislike":2,"score":221,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T11:12:05.000Z","msg":"唔好捉我返入去呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d14c94338cf359aa0b81f8a4e6a260f808e997d","tid":1056680,"uid":201604,"like":32,"dislike":2,"score":30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T11:12:05.000